Sarri on Loftus-Cheek improvement: &quot;He has improved a lot, especially tactically. Now tactically he is a very good midfielder. At the beginning of the season he was a very offensive midfielder. Now he is complete, I think&quot; <br />
<br />
Sarri on Loftus-Cheek's back and future: &quot;Maybe but we need to check every day the condition of his back. Today, he had only a recovery session because he needs time to recover after the match. The only problem with him is probably that he can't play for 90 minutes.&quot;

Chelsea are close to a deal to sign Sweden's 15 year old rising star, Edwin Andersson.<br />
